title: Brady vs. Brees Part 2, Russ vs. Buffalo, and More Week 9 Bets | Ringer NFL Show
description:
We recap the Packers-49ers 'Thursday Night Football' game (2:00), discuss how to consider injuries when betting early lines (23:00), and dive into the top Week 9 games to wager on (36:00).
